node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Christy Mack on September 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Today I had the opportunity to visit and learn about Xunantunich. 

I can't wait to see more and share my adventure this week, mostly in my stories and Belize highlight on my page!
